            <title><![CDATA[国民党空间重设计 门口摆“天下为公”屏风]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202102/20210224/20210224_tw_guo_min_dang_.jpg?itok=4sO_xoP6" title="国民党空间重设计，门口摆“天下为公”屏风。（互联网）" alt src="https://www.zaobao.com.sg/sites/default/files/styles/article_large_full/public/images/202102/20210224/20210224_tw_guo_min_dang_.jpg?itok=4sO_xoP6" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><figcaption>国民党空间重设计，门口摆“天下为公”屏风。（互联网）</figcaption>

<p>国民党更新中央党部一楼景观，入口处未来将设置大型屏风，写上国民党总理、国父孙中山先生墨宝“天下为公”、“努力进前”，勉励党务工作同仁秉持民本精神、事事与人民站在一起，也期许党务运作顺畅。</p>

